questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?count) WHERE { { ?uri dbo:location dbr:South_Carolina ; rdf:type dbo:Lake } UNION { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Rivers_and_streams_of_South_Carolina } }

questions.question: Is Pluto really a planet?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> ASK WHERE { dbr:Pluto rdf:type dbo:Planet }

questions.question: What is the largest state in the United States?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dct:subject dbc:States_of_the_United_States ; rdf:type dbo:AdministrativeRegion ; dbo:areaTotal ?area } ORDER BY DESC(?area) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

questions.question: What is the wavelength of indigo?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?n WHERE { dbr:Indigo dbo:wavelength ?n }

questions.question: What was the name of the famous battle in 1836 in San Antonio?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:MilitaryConflict ; dbo:place dbr:San_Antonio ; dbo:date ?date FILTER ( ?date > "1835-12-31T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) FILTER ( ?date <= "1836-12-31T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) }

questions.question: When did Muhammad die?

questions.question: When was the De Beers company founded?

questions.question: Which American presidents were in office during the Vietnam War?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Vietnam_War dbo:commander ?uri . ?uri dct:subject res:Category:Presidents_of_the_United_States }

questions.question: Who killed Caesar?

questions.question: How big is the earth's diameter?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT (( xsd:double(?radius) * 2 ) AS ?diameter) WHERE { res:Earth dbo:meanRadius ?radius }

questions.question: Which museum exhibits The Scream by Munch?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:The_Scream dbo:museum ?uri }

questions.question: Give me a list of all critically endangered birds.

questions.question: Which book has the most pages?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Book ; dbo:numberOfPages ?n } ORDER BY DESC(?n) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
